{"about_the_game":"After his mother goes missing, a young man and his older brother travel to the small town called Free Will, where she was last seen.<br>Things get complicated very quickly when he is drawn into a chain of events that takes place in the town and meets the person he thought he would never see again.<br>As his stay in town continues, he's going to question his previous decisions and begin to see the true value in life.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743260/extras/steam_picture1.png?t=1670112723\" /><br><br>Welcome to Free Will is a Visual Novel (VN) game where every choice you make has an impact on the story and relations with the characters.<br>You play as a young man who's about to finish college and doesn't really know what to do with his life. You are the one who's going to guide him through this experience. Will you be the guy who just wanna have some fun? Or are you looking for something more? The town hides many secrets... and many beautiful women.<br>This is a mature story about growing into your adult life and finding your path. Shape your own future!<br><br>In this game, you have a phone where you can write messages, make calls, check stats or listen to music. Also, you have a journal where you can read your diary or check the unlocked renders. In the open section of the game, you can find special renders, money, gazettes, magazines to read, and more. There are also optional minigames.<br>As you can see there's plenty to do - and I have even more things planned for the future<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743260/extras/steam_picture2.png?t=1670112723\" /><br><br>Episode 1 - Small World:<br><i>After 4 years with no contact, your brother visits you saying that your mother is missing. You go with him to find her, not knowing that this decision will change your life completely.</i><br><br>- An immersive world, with characters that you care about.<br>- A non-linear storyline where every choice matters.<br>- High-quality renders and animations.<br>- Optional mini-games and collectible side story.<br>- Special renders to unlock.<br>- Amazing soundtrack that makes you jump right into this world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743260/extras/steam_picture3.png?t=1670112723\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Small World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/c50bf5ebf63bcf833adfd98ccc262dd5fb258c00.jpg"},{"name":"Adventure","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/76131d9f6fbfd2831655c9c92b055c5ca30c0f1f.jpg"},{"name":"Tell me everything!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/9e7ce89d31710506070fae6e0bf45a1a707fb3cd.jpg"},{"name":"Broken Heart","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/9fda8d8b7c1002bd91129121ca3d9f04c77ffc0e.jpg"},{"name":"Medic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/8577cd68fc74d128ee63af02cb6e77f88e7a0a3a.jpg"},{"name":"I'm just here to watch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/90363ba27ea2e7316cd01dae3cd11cd0d5eb9d3a.jpg"},{"name":"The Uncle Method","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/e879c041371593450f10d229b9db4bec52cbe0b8.jpg"},{"name":"I'm just here to impress","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/7903bebec4f189bf6daa21ac61f0ecf1b666fab8.jpg"},{"name":"Gym Freak","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1743260/e2e9d06edaa35a379c520ae96f36a759b0f26aec.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to White Diamond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/imag